reviewText: This is an obscure but interesting documentary. I notice that Amazon has almost no interest in including such offerings in its video stable. I would happily pay to view through  Amazon.

3 Minutes to Impact is a highly informative while entertaining documentary that brings together the latest in the burgeoning young science of meteorite and asteroid impact events. As a prospective impact geologist, I  highly recommend this documentary for those with a strong intrest in impact  science and to those with just a general intrest in the sciences.
